 and language register.
 Literature, due to its inherent freedom of writing, does not need to follow
 any pattern or rule that can help us to structure the unstructured.
 Examples of more structured texts are scientific papers, patent texts,
 health diagnostics, etc.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Nevertheless, depending on how the text is treated and processed, the nature
